Setting up a SalesForce Android project

Follow the instructions to install the prerequisites, the Mobile SDK and to create a native project:
   https://developer.salesforce.com/mobile/getting-started/android/ 
   
Navigate to the library projects and the app project in the following order:
 1. Cordova
 2. SalesForceSDK
 3. <app>
 
 In each of the projects, execute the following commands:
  1. android update project -p . -t <id> 
     -<id> is the id of the target android SDK
     -to see the installed SDKs and their IDs run:  android list target
  2. ant clean debug